status_message: Being published from the Middle East, especially from Saudi Arabia, allows one to be at the center of almost everything. Whether it has been the Kingdom's road to economic development, the first Saudi astronaut in space or social changes in Saudi society, whether its the Arab-Israeli conflict, the Cold War, the Gulf War or the invasion of  Afghanistan & Iraq, under the guise of "War on terror" or the elimination of leadership through assassination (Rafiq Harriri) or execution (Saddam Hussein). Arab News is at the center of the world, at the center of Middle East, at the center change. In short, Arab News is......at the center of it all.
link_name: 30 years in 30 seconds
